This is a command line tool to edit contact list and publish presence.
It works on python 3.2 and should work on > python 3.0 and possibly > python 2.7 (not tested yet)

Usage:
- to setup the tool call "python setup.py"

You need to have a configuration file (works on mobile config, should work with pc config)
- to get config file call "python get.py" to see usage

To use the client for something useful
- to manage presence call "python presence.py" to see usage
- to manage roster call "python roster.py" to see usage